node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Igor Jones on September 01, 2021. May be an image of text that says '6 Things we wish we did in our 20s. Presented by @businessmotivationfamily Via: @brianandgab'.

Photo by Igor Jones on September 01, 2021. May be an image of text that says '1. Manage your time. You're not overwhelmed, you're unorganized. -Wake up earlier -Create a to-do list list -Set deadlines -Stick to your schedule'.
Photo by Igor Jones on September 01, 2021. May be an image of text that says '2. Stop looking for a new thing. -a new job -A new city -a new bartner Make something out of your current situao first.'.

Photo by Igor Jones on September 01, 2021. May be an image of text that says '3. Focus on one thing. Everyone wants results, but nobody wants to stay focused The gap between your current life and the life you want is called the focus. Focus 100% on one thing instead of doing 5 things with 20% focus each.'.

Photo by Igor Jones on September 01, 2021. May be an image of text that says '4. Make gradual improvements. You can't go to eve level 10 with level 1 habits. -Start by reading one page -Start by writing one paragraph -Start by doing one workout -Start today Then focus on getting 1% better every day. Minor improvements over time lead to big changes.'.

Photo by Igor Jones on September 01, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5. Stop chasing motivation. Your motivation is not the problem. Its your discipline that's holding you back. -Stay consistent -Meet your own deadlines -Find an accountability partne Long-term discipline and consistency are far more important than short- term intensity.'.

Photo by Igor Jones on September 01, 2021. May be an image of text that says '6. Find your purpose. Without direction or a clear plan, it's hard to live a fulfilled life. Everything in life becomes easier once you find your purpose and get clarity on what's next.'.
Photo by Igor Jones on August 31, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, car and text that says 'BMF Be the person with $100k in the bank and a $5k car. Not $5k in the bank and a $100k car.'.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Igor Jones on August 30, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Don't Do These You Want To Be Rich Presented by @businessmotivationfamily Created by @awareness_of_success'.

Photo by Igor Jones on August 30, 2021. May be an image of text that says '1. Waking Up Late Get a headstart with your day by waking up early. Create a strong morning routine and be at your maximum productivity. 2. Poor Hygiene It will negatively affect your ability to network with people who may help you to be successful.'.

Photo by Igor Jones on August 30, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says '3. Not Taking Accountability For Your Failures Although your success can be affected by your circumstances, 90% of your success relies on YOU. 4. Thinking others Should Help You Nobody owes you anything. Nobody will solve your problems for you. You must take charge of your life and don't blame others.'.

Photo by Igor Jones on August 30, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5. Watching Too Much Netflix or TV This type of escapism can take hours of your day. Hours that should have been spent on things that could bring you closer to your goals. 6. Being Too Consumed With Sports It might be entertaining, but it only benefits the players and not you.'.

Photo by Igor Jones on August 30, 2021. May be an image of text that says '7. Having No Savings If you don't have an emergency fund, then your properties are always in danger of liquidation, or you may need loans. 8. Surrounding Yourself With Poor People You are the sum of the five people you spend the most time with. Poor people will reinforce your poor habits and beliefs.'.

Photo by Igor Jones on August 30, 2021. May be an image of text that says '9. Eating Junk And Fast Food It makes you feel sluggish at work and clouds your judgment. Be careful of what you take in. Food has a direct effect on how your body and mind function. 10. Not Following Through With Your Goals Take action and strategically think out your plan. It's not enough to have dreams. You must also put in the work.'.
Photo by Igor Jones on August 30, 2021. May be an image of phone, screen and text.
